Insider Activity


Individual




James G. Berges



Mr. James G. Berges is Chairman at HD Supply, Inc., Partner at Clayton Dubilier & Rice LLC, Independent Director at PPG Industries, Inc., Chairman at HD Supply Holdings, Inc., and Chairman at Hussmann International, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Atkore International Holdings, Inc., NCI Building Systems, Inc., PPG Industries, Inc., Atkore International Group, Inc., and Atkore International, Inc. He joined Clayton Dubilier & Rice in 2006.
Mr. Berges was previously employed as Chairman by Sally Beauty Holdings, Inc., President by Emerson Electric Co., Chairman by Sally Holdings LLC, and a Member by Sally Investment Holdings LLC. He also served on the board at Diversey, Inc., MKS Instruments, Inc., and Diversey Holdings, Inc.
Mr. Berges holds a B.S. in Electrical Engineering from the University of Notre Dame.



